 {"id":"flywheel_connectors-j05nu.7.3","title":"Outlook / Exchange: readiness, compliance, verification, and operator guidance","description":"Finish Outlook or Exchange with readiness and doctor outputs, tenant and mailbox remediation guidance, deterministic tests across mail and calendar workflows, and explicit V3 compliance evidence for a communication connector with both read and risky mutation semantics.","acceptance_criteria":"- closeout requires comprehensive deterministic unit coverage for auth, timeout, retry, error-mapping, pagination or state transitions, and the highest-risk provider-specific mutations\n- closeout requires archetype-appropriate integration coverage built on shared `fcp-testkit` helpers rather than connector-local one-offs\n- closeout requires at least one replayable E2E or host-backed verification script that runs through `rch`, captures detailed structured logs, and preserves manifest, readiness, doctor, and conformance artifacts\n- operator guidance must name prerequisites, dedicated environments, redaction rules, common remediation paths, and rerun commands for the verification bundle\n- evidence attached to the bead must be sufficient for a future agent to rerun verification without reopening external planning notes","status":"open","priority":2,"issue_type":"task","created_at":"2026-03-18T01:22:24.726334Z","created_by":"jemanuel","updated_at":"2026-03-18T06:28:29.532590Z","source_repo":".","compaction_level":0,"original_size":0,"dependencies":[{"issue_id":"flywheel_connectors-j05nu.7.3","depends_on_id":"flywheel_connectors-j05nu.7","type":"parent-child","created_at":"2026-03-18T01:22:24.726334Z","created_by":"jemanuel","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""},{"issue_id":"flywheel_connectors-j05nu.7.3","depends_on_id":"flywheel_connectors-j05nu.7.2","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-03-18T01:22:24.726334Z","created_by":"jemanuel","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""},{"issue_id":"flywheel_connectors-j05nu.7.3","depends_on_id":"flywheel_connectors