 {"id":"flywheel_connectors-j05nu.8","title":"[T3-NICHE] Tier 3 Niche & Emerging: Mastodon, HN, Wolfram, Maps, Twitch, LINE, Feishu","description":"Niche and emerging platform connectors. Lower priority but valuable for specific user segments. Mastodon/ActivityPub: decentralized social, growing post-Twitter. Hacker News: developer community. Wolfram Alpha: computational knowledge. OpenStreetMap/Mapbox: geospatial. Twitch: live streaming (OpenClaw supports it). LINE: 200M+ users in Japan/Taiwan/Thailand. Feishu/Lark: ByteDance workplace platform, growing in APAC.","status":"closed","priority":3,"issue_type":"epic","created_at":"2026-03-17T22:04:28.383070Z","created_by":"jemanuel","updated_at":"2026-03-23T07:50:44.922937Z","closed_at":"2026-03-23T07:50:44.922937Z","close_reason":"All 7 children closed. Tier 3 Niche connectors epic complete.","source_repo":".","compaction_level":0,"original_size":0,"dependencies":[{"issue_id":"flywheel_connectors-j05nu.8","depends_on_id":"flywheel_connectors-j05nu","type":"parent-child","created_at":"2026-03-17T22:04:28.383070Z","created_by":"jemanuel","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""}]}
 {"id":"flywheel_connectors-j05nu.8.1","title":"[T3-NICHE.1] fcp.mastodon \u2014 Mastodon/ActivityPub Connector","description":"Mastodon decentralized social connector via Mastodon REST API. Operations: mastodon.statuses.post/get/delete/boost/favourite, mastodon.timeline.home/public/tag, mastodon.accounts.get/follow/unfollow/search, mastodon.notifications.list/get/dismiss, mastodon.search (full-text across posts/accounts/hashtags), mastodon.lists.list/get/create. Auth: OAuth2 (app registration on target instance). Network: configurable instance URL (e.g., mastodon.social). REST API. Post/delete=Risky, reads=Safe. 3 subtasks.","status":"closed","priority":3,"issue_type":"feature","created_at":"2026-03-17T22:04:41.591155Z","created_by":"jemanuel","updated_at":"2026-03-23T07:50:03.103144Z","closed_at":"2026-03-23T07:50:03.103144Z","close_reason":"All children closed. Epic complete.","source_repo":".","compaction_level":0,"original_size":0,"dependencies":[{"issue_id":"flywheel_connectors-j05nu.8.1","depends_on_id":"flywheel_connectors-j05nu.8","type":"parent-child","created_at":"2026-03-17T22:04:41.591155Z","created_by":"jemanuel","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""}],"comments":[{"id":1809,"issue_id":"flywheel_connectors-j05nu.8.1","author":"jemanuel","text":"Testing requirements: 50+ unit tests (wiremock), 10+ integration tests (ConnectorSuite/ComplianceSuite), E2E compliance script, structured JSON logging with connector_id/operation_id/duration_ms, retry telemetry with attempt/delay_ms/error. All tests deterministic, no real API calls, no timing-based flakiness.","created_at":"2026-03-18T00:25:09Z"}]}
